    "synopsis": "As Hive Fleet Leviathan grinds toward Baal, Blood Angels Sergeant Jatiel and his squad keep a lonely vigil over a dead world far from the front. When their ship crashes and draws the swarm down upon them, the survivors are driven underground — straight into the path of the necron overlord Anrakyr the Traveller, who has come to wake a slumbering tomb. With the tyranids hungering above, ancient enemies forge a desperate, uneasy alliance to survive the dark beneath the surface, and the battle for the Cryptus shieldworlds reaches its close.",
